An example app showing pagination and ember-data + django rest framework

To run this django application

1. pip install -r requirements.txt
2. python manage.py runserver

If you just want to see the ember part of this project

https://github.com/toranb/ember-django-pagination/blob/master/ember/static/script/app/person.js

If you want to see the handelbars template for the above

https://github.com/toranb/ember-django-pagination/blob/master/ember/person/templates/index.html
